data.description: Great Price for this oversized  Westchester Model one of the largest in the community with a single car garage. This home features a Florida Room open to a Den, full size dining room, upgraded kitchen and appliances, xl Bonus room can be used as a 3rd bedroom or an oversized home office. New  AC. new permitted screened patio for relaxing  with rolled down shades for privacy , new electrical panel, water heater ,washer and dryer  One occupant must be 55+ and no occupants under 18. Association requires $40,000 annual income and a credit score of 700  No leasing in 1st year of ownership. Price reflects sellers motivation.  Low association fees includes lawncare , pool, park and clubhouse. Great location near Turnpike and I-95 See this spacious home today!
